<script>
export default {
  name: 'headPart',
  data(){
    return {activeIndex: '1'}
  },
  methods:{
    switchtore () {
      this.$router.push('/home')
    },
    handleSelect(key, keyPath) {
        switch(key)
        {
          case '1':
            this.$router.push('/home')
            break
          case '2':
            this.$router.push('/register')
            break
          case '8':
            this.$router.push('/template')
            break
        }
          
        
        console.log(keyPath)
    }
  }

}
</script>

<style scoped>

.router-link-active {
  text-decoration: none;
}
a {
  text-decoration: none;
}
</style>
